    <author>
      <name>Yan Liu, Jingmai Wang, Yulan Wang, Dan Zhang</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;b&gt;Marketing Science&lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;This paper examines how coalition loyalty programs enhance firms’ ability to price discriminate and shows why the optimal program size depends on market composition.</content>
